# 26 USC 32(e) - Taxable Year Must Be Full Taxable Year
#
status: boilerplate
notes: "Administrative requirement - no computational content"

text: """
(e) Taxable year must be full taxable year
Except in the case of a taxable year closed by reason of the death of
the taxpayer, no credit shall be allowable under this section in the case
of a taxable year covering a period of less than 12 months.
"""
